        <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;">除非本协议另有约定，在本协议中所用下列术语定义如下</span><span lang="EN-US">:</span></p>
