        <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">1.3<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;">甲方：指在服务平台上寻找服务</span><span lang="EN-US">/</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;">产品并支付费用的用户。</span></p>
