        <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">1.6<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;">平台账户：指用户在服务平台注册的帐号，用户只能通过该帐户登陆服务平台进行交易。</span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
